articles.title: Biden warns most COVID-related deaths this year will be result of people not being updated on their vaccines - Fox News
articles.description: President Biden gave a press conference Tuesday urging Americans to get their updated COVID-19 vaccines and prevent more unnecessary deaths.
articles.content:
